Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives
William Asadorian Collection TAM 461
13.5 Linear Feet in 26 boxes
1720-2011 The bulk of materials in this collection are in English. Several items are in Russian. Flate File 8 Drawer 10 (with Hershkowitz materials)
Immediate Source of Acquisition
Materials donated by William Asadorian and Ronald Asadorian in 2008, 2009, 2010, 2011, 2016, and 2008; additional materials were found in the repository inn 2009, 2011, and 2017. The accession numbers related to this collection are 2008.052, 2009.017, 2009.018, 2009.022, 2009.028, 2009.029, 2009.034, 2009.042, 2009.045, 2009.098, 2009.099, 2010.055, 2010.084, 2011.051, 2011.116, 2011.125, 2011.130, 2011.141, 2016.059, 2017.065, and 2018. 010.
Preferred Citation
Identification of item, date; William Asadorian Collection; TAM 461; box number; folder number; Tamiment Library/Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives, New York University.
Conditions Governing Use
Because of the assembled nature of this collection, copyright status varies across the collection. Copyright is assumed to be held by the original creator of individual items in the collection; these items are expected to pass into the public domain 120 years after their creation. The Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archive is not authorized to grant permission to publish or reproduce materials from this collection.
